record_source.ref: SELECT tbl_KD_Kundenstamm.* FROM tbl_KD_Kundenstamm ORDER BY tbl_KD_Kundenstamm.kun_Firma;

row_source.ref: SELECT "_ALLE" AS kun_Ort, "Alle" AS kun_plz FROM tbl_KD_Kundenstamm WHERE kun_ID = 11100 UNION SELECT * From qryHlp_KunOrt ORDER BY kun_ort;
SELECT [_tblLKZ].ISO_2 AS LKZ, [_tblLKZ].Landesname_deu AS Staat, [_tblLKZ].Euro, [_tblLKZ].TelVorwahl AS Landesvorwahl, "Postfach" AS Postfachtxt FROM _tblLKZ;

SELECT tbl_KD_Kundenstamm.kun_Id, tbl_KD_Kundenstamm.kun_Firma, tbl_KD_Ansprechpartner.adr_Nachname, tbl_KD_Ansprechpartner.adr_Vorname, tbl_KD_Ansprechpartner.adr_Handy FROM tbl_KD_Kundenstamm LEFT JOIN tbl_KD_Ansprechpartner ON tbl_KD_Kundenstamm.kun_IDF_PersonID = tbl_KD_Ansprechpartner.adr_ID WHERE kun_IstAktiv = TRUE ORDER BY kun_firma;
SELECT tbl_KD_Kundenstamm.kun_Id, tbl_KD_Kundenstamm.kun_Firma FROM tbl_KD_Kundenstamm ORDER BY tbl_KD_Kundenstamm.kun_Firma;
